author: Laura Hughes
title: Vince Cable received 'bizarre' 5am phone calls from Gordon Brown
text: Politics Vince Cable received 'bizarre' 5am phone calls from Gordon Brown Sir Vince told an audience at the Henley Literary Festival that by the end of his time as leader of the Labour Party, Mr Brown had become 'extraordinarily depressed' Gordon Brown would call up Sir Vince Cable for "bizarre conversations" Photo: Jeff J Mitchell/Getty Images By Laura Hughes , Political Correspondent 8:40AM BST 02 Oct 2015
